<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Building a $5K/Month Digital Product Business in 10 Days — ZOO Blog</title>
<meta name="description" content="The exact playbook: product research → creation → Stripe checkout → cold outreach → first revenue. Real numbers, real timeline.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,400;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--black:#060608;--surface:#121214;--border:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);--text:#e8e6e3;--text-dim:#6a6a6a;--text-muted:#3a3a3a;--accent:#c9a96e;--accent-glow:rgba(201,169,110,0.15);--green:#22c55e;--font-serif:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;--font-sans:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;--ease:cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)}
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{background:var(--black);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
body{font-family:var(--font-sans);background:var(--black);color:var(--text);line-height:1.7}
::selection{background:var(--accent);color:#000}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px}::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--black)}::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#1a1a1a}
.nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:1000;padding:24px 48px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;transition:all 0.6s var(--ease)}
.nav.scrolled{padding:14px 48px;background:rgba(6,6,8,0.95);backdrop-filter:blur(40px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.nav-logo{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);text-decoration:none;font-style:italic}
.nav-logo em{color:var(--accent);font-style:italic}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;list-style:none;align-items:center}
.nav-links a{color:var(--text-dim);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:500;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.14em;transition:color 0.3s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}
.nav-cta{padding:10px 22px;border:1px solid var(--accent);border-radius:100px;color:var(--accent);background:transparent;font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.4s var(--ease);font-family:var(--font-sans)}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(--accent);color:#000}
.article-hero{padding:160px 48px 60px;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto}
.article-eyebrow{font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:16px}
.article-title{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,4.5vw,3rem);font-weight:900;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:20px}
.article-meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;margin-bottom:40px;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-dim)}
.article-hero-img{width:100%;height:320px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;filter:grayscale(30%) contrast(1.05);margin-bottom:48px}
.article-body{max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 48px 120px}
.article-body h2{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin:48px 0 16px;line-height:1.3}
.article-body p{color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:20px;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.8}
.article-body strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:600}
.article-body ul{margin:16px 0 24px;padding-left:24px}
.article-body li{color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:8px;font-size:0.92rem}
.article-body li::marker{color:var(--accent)}
blockquote{border-left:3px solid var(--accent);padding:16px 24px;margin:32px 0;background:var(--accent-glow);border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;font-style:italic;color:var(--text)}
.cta-box{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:36px;margin:48px 0;text-align:center}
.cta-box h3{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px}
.cta-box p{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:24px}
.cta-box .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 28px;background:var(--accent);color:#000;border-radius:10px;font-weight:600;font-size:0.85rem;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.3s;font-family:var(--font-sans)}
.cta-box .btn:hover{background:#dbc08a;transform:translateY(-1px)}
.footer{padding:48px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);text-align:center}
.footer p{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.78rem}
.footer a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none}
@media(max-width:768px){
  .nav{padding:16px 20px}.nav-links{display:none}
  .article-hero{padding:120px 20px 40px}
  .article-hero-img{height:200px}
  .article-body{padding:0 20px 80px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="nav" id="nav">
  <a href="/index.html" class="nav-logo">ZOO<em>.</em></a>
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:32px">
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="/products.html">Products</a></li>
      <li><a href="/blog.html">Blog</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="/checkout.html" class="nav-cta">Shop</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<article>
  <header class="article-hero">
    <div class="article-eyebrow">Growth — Strategy</div>
    <h1 class="article-title">Building a $5K/Month Digital Product Business in 10 Days</h1>
    <div class="article-meta">
      <span>📅 May 8, 2026</span>
      <span>⏱ 7 min read</span>
      <span>💰 Playbook</span>
    </div>
    <img class="article-hero-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?w=900&q=80" alt="Digital Products">
  </header>

  <div class="article-body">
    <p>Can you really build a $5K/month digital product business in 10 days? We're finding out — in real time, with real numbers, and full transparency.</p>

    <p>Here's the playbook we're following at ZOO. Every step, every number, every lesson learned.</p>

    <h2>Day 1: Research + Product Selection</h2>
    <p>We scanned HN, Indie Hackers, and GitHub Trending to identify 5 high-demand, low-competition digital products:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Notion Template Pack for Founders</strong> ($19/$29) — 100K+ Notion users searching for founder templates</li>
      <li><strong>AI Agent Starter Kit</strong> ($49) — Exploding demand, few production-ready options</li>
      <li><strong>Landing Page Templates</strong> ($29) — Evergreen demand, premium positioning</li>
      <li><strong>Trading EA Templates</strong> ($49) — Niche audience, high willingness to pay</li>
      <li><strong>API Boilerplate</strong> ($39) — Every dev needs this, nobody wants to build it</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Day 1 (afternoon): Build + Package</h2>
    <p>Using AI agent orchestration, we built all 5 products in parallel. Each product includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Production-ready code/templates</li>
      <li>Professional sales page with Stripe checkout</li>
      <li>Documentation and getting-started guide</li>
      <li>License for commercial use</li>
    </ul>

    <blockquote>"The bottleneck isn't building — it's distribution. Anyone can build a product. Few can sell it."</blockquote>

    <h2>Day 1 (evening): Outreach + Distribution</h2>
    <p>We sent 183+ cold outreach emails to YC companies, startups, and potential partners. Each email was personalized with a specific growth idea for their product.</p>

    <p>Results after Day 1:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>1 response</strong> from Wilco Kruijer (ReJot) — hot lead</li>
      <li><strong>2 products</strong> with live Stripe checkout</li>
      <li><strong>3 products</strong> pending Payment Links (Stripe Dashboard workaround)</li>
      <li><strong>$0 revenue</strong> (expected on Day 1)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>The Math</h2>
    <p>To hit $5K in 9 remaining days ($556/day):</p>
    <ul>
      <li>At $49/product: need ~12 sales/day</li>
      <li>At 2% email conversion: need 600 emails/day</li>
      <li>With 5 products at different price points: blended target is achievable</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What's Next</h2>
    <p>Days 2-3: Scale outreach, activate backup channels (Ko-fi, Gumroad), follow up with hot leads. Days 4-5: ProductHunt launch. Days 6-10: Optimize conversion, double down on what works.</p>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <h3>Follow the Journey</h3>
      <p>We're building in public. Get our products, follow our progress, and learn from our playbook.</p>
      <a href="/products.html" class="btn">Browse Products →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

<footer class="footer">
  <p>© 2026 <a href="/index.html">ZOO Technologies</a>. Built with autonomous agents.</p>
</footer>

<script>
window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
  document.getElementById('nav').classList.toggle('scrolled', window.scrollY > 60);
}, { passive: true });
</script>
</body>
</html>
